author: A_Brickset_user
title: pretty cool
review: this is probably the coolest of the dinosaur sets. the styracosaurus looks really cool, the horns are nice, and on the back of the dinosaur set poster is an environment poster that the dinosaur can live on. it is a great. set. 10

author: Tyrannosaurus23
title: Great
review:
It's a really good set and the pieces are rare. I'll move on to the pros and cons now....

 

  • Pros:
  • Rare pieces
  • Fun to play with the other dinosaurs with

 

  • Cons:
  • Tail is short
  • The Camarasaurus doesn't look completely accurate

author: KLOKRIECHER
title: LEGO Dinosaurs - Styracosaurus Review
review:
This is my 3rd favourite set of the LEGO Dinosaurs theme. It doesn't have any stickers which means that these bricks which we get in this set are valuable. We don't get many play features but we're able to build 3 more dinosaurs with the pieces of this model. I like the design which LEGO has given this creature. The LEGO Dinosaurs theme is not a theme for the older kids and for the adult. It's more something which the younger kids will enjoy more. But the pieces we get here can be helpful for the older kids and for the adults for some future MOC's (My own creations) and/or brickfilms for sure...

All in all this set is an okay set and I would recommend you to get this. You can find this set on eBay, BrickLink and Amazon for sure. Here is the link where you can check out the full gallery I made for this set on my website: http://www.klokriecher.de
